<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM5.4">
<l>eṉpuru kiyiṉa vēlneṭuṅ kaṇka ḷimaiporun tāpala nāḷum</l>
<l>tuṉpak kaṭalpukku vaikunta ṉeṉpatōr tōṇi peṟātuḻal kiṉṟēṉ</l>
<l>aṉpuṭai yāraip pirivuṟu nōyatu nīyu maṟiti kuyilē</l>
<l>poṉpurai mēṉik karuḷak koṭiyuṭaip puṇṇiya ṉaivarak kūvāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The bones have melted; the eyelids of spear-like long eyes will not touch;</l>
<l>Having entered the ocean of miseries a long time [ago],</l>
<l rend="indent">I am whirling around [in it] not obtaining the unique raft</l>
<l rend="indent">called [the Lord of] Vaikuṇṭha.</l>
<l>O koel, you too know the pain of suffering [that comes] from parting from the loved ones!</l>
<l>Cry so that the Holy [Lord]—whose body is akin to gold and whose banner is Garuḍa—comes!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
